My build of sent, the simple plaintext presentation tool by suckless.org

# Patches applied
- progress bar
- toggle cursor

# Requirements
- Xlib
- Xft
- farbfeld

# Installation
git clone https://github.com/baj0k/SB
cd SB/sent
sudo make install

# Recompilation
sudo make clean install

# Usage
$ sent [FILE]

If FILE is omitted or equals `-`, stdin will be read.
Each paragraph represents one slide.
Paragraphs starting with `@` in front of the filename produce image slide
Lines starting with `#` will be ignored
You can escape '@' and '#' with `\`
